name: FTargetDeviceUnclaimed
doc:
Implements a message that is sent when a device is no longer claimed.

@see FTargetDeviceClaimDenied, FTargetDeviceClaimRequest

DeviceName: Holds the identifier of the device that is no longer claimed.
HostName: Holds the name of the host computer that had claimed the device.
HostUser: Holds the name of the user that had claimed the device.
